make&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: Leaving directory `/root/rpmbuild/BUILD/e2fsprogs-1.41.90.wc3/lib/ext2fs&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
